com.deltaxml.cores9api

Interface DocumentProgressListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PipelineProgressListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DCPipelineProgressTextReporter

    public interface DocumentProgressListener
extends PipelineProgressListener
    Monitor the progress of the document comparator. This extends the pipelined comparator's progress listener with four additional messages, for reporting the Start and Finish of the flattening pre-processing stages for both 'A' and 'B' inputs.
    Since:
    7.0
